# -*- mode: org -*-

** vNEXT

**** Remove ~kanit-regular.ttf~
This change falls back onto standard web fonts across all
languages. This should help decrease bundle size, and save
time processing the custom font during page load

**** Add src/js/main/vendor.ts
Add a new entry point that bundles preact, and other third
party dependencies. Third-party imports are now in a single
place rather than duplicated throughout app components

**** Reduce bundle size
This change removes build artifacts and features that don't
apply on KaiOS (such as opengraph)

**** Replace the play, pause icons
This change replaces the previous icons with a set of icons
compatible with KaiOS

**** Remove nanoc-gzip.rb
This change removes a network optimization that doesn't apply when
resources are local to the device

**** Remove loaders
This change removes all loaders from ~/src/js/loaders/~, and
the postman package (~packages/typescript/postman~). Resources
are local to the device, and that reduces how useful the loader
feature can be

**** KaiOS fork
This change forks a new branch: ~kaios/main~. The branch will be
dedicated to KaiOS support, and diverges from the ~main~ branch

**** Add ~etc/~
This change moves a large portion of the website's configuration
files to the ~/etc~ directory


** v0.9.0

**** Add ~share/al-quran.reflectslight.io/documentation/~
This change replaces ~share/doc/al-quran.reflectslight.io~
**** Add new recitation
A new recitation by Hani ar-Rifai has been added

**** Replace ~opengraph.rb~ with ~_opengraph.html.erb~
This change simplifies how we render opengraph-related meta tags

**** Move to nodejs for scss compiler
This change replaces the deprecated Ruby scss compiler with the
nodejs compiler

**** Add ~audio.base_url~ to nanoc.yaml
This change provides increased flexibility in how the website
serve audio files

**** Rename packages/typescript/Quran/ properties
This change introduces urlName, translitName to Surah objects

**** eslint upgrade
This change migrates to the most recent version of eslint (^9.8)
